== 制作 ==
2017年，[[法蘭絲·麥杜雯|法蘭絲·麥杜雯]]在阅读《游牧人生》一书后深受喜欢，后与{{le|彼得·斯皮尔斯|Peter Spears}}买下了该书的电影改编权，同年在[[2017年多倫多國際影展|第42届多倫多國際影展]]观看赵婷执导的《[[骑士_(电影)|骑士]]》一片后即表示要与其合作。2018年3月，两人在{{le|第33届独立精神奖|33rd Independent Spirit Awards}}颁奖典礼会面，达成了改编《无依之地》的协议<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.goldderby.com/article/2020/chloe-zhao-nomadland-interview/|title= Frances McDormand is the reason that Chloe Zhao made ‘Nomadland’|website= Gold Derby|first= Susan|last= King|date= 2020-12-31|access-date= 2021-01-20|archive-date= 2021-01-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210104195537/https://www.goldderby.com/article/2020/chloe-zhao-nomadland-interview/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

2019年2月，法蘭絲·麥杜雯，[[大衛·史崔森|大衛·史崔森]]，琳达·梅和夏琳·史旺奇宣布加入了该片的演员阵容，[[趙婷_(導演)|趙婷]]执导并改编杰西卡·布劳德的報導文學《{{le|游牧人生 (報導文學)|Nomadland (book)|游牧人生}}》。[[法蘭絲·麥杜雯|法蘭絲·麥杜雯]]，{{le|彼得·斯皮尔斯|Peter Spears}}，莫利·阿舍，丹·简维和趙婷担任制片，[[探照灯影业|探照灯影业]]负责该片北美方面的发行（海外方面由[[华特迪士尼工作室电影|华特迪士尼工作室电影]]负责发行）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/chloe-zhao-nomadland-frances-mcdormand-fox-searchlight-acquisition-1202555791/|title=Chloé Zhao’s ‘Nomadland’ Starring Frances McDormand Lands At Fox Searchlight|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2019-02-12|accessdate=2019-02-12|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826154815/https://deadline.com/2019/02/chloe-zhao-nomadland-frances-mcdormand-fox-searchlight-acquisition-1202555791/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.foxsearchlight.com/post/4321/fox-searchlight-pictures-acquires-worldwide-rights-to-chloe-zhaos-nomadland-with-frances-mcdormand/|title=FOX SEARCHLIGHT PICTURES ACQUIRES WORLDWIDE RIGHTS TO CHLOÉ ZHAO’S “NOMADLAND” WITH FRANCES MCDORMAND|website=Fox Searchlight|access-date=2019-02-15|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903081302/https://www.searchlightpictures.com/post/4321/fox-searchlight-pictures-acquires-worldwide-rights-to-chloe-zhaos-nomadland-with-frances-mcdormand/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

