== 辱华风波 ==
{{see also|趙婷#中國審查}}
影片原计划于2021年4月23日在中国大陆上映<ref>{{cite web |title=赵婷 《无依之地》4月23日上映 |url=http://paper.zbnews.net/zbwb/pc/content/202103/03/content_16471.html |website=淄博晚报 |accessdate=2022-02-18 |date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2022-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220218135712/http://paper.zbnews.net/zbwb/pc/content/202103/03/content_16471.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=《无依之地》定档4月国内上映 |url=http://cq.china.com.cn/2021-02/24/content_41475581.html |website=中国网-华龙网 |accessdate=2022-02-18 |archive-date=2022-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220611153945/http://cq.china.com.cn/2021-02/24/content_41475581.html }}</ref>。中国媒体本来对赵婷得奖一事大肆赞扬，随着时间的推移她在过往言论被网友翻出，其中一句「中国是一个充满谎言的国家」。中国民间便集体抵制这部电影<ref>{{cite web |title=【從中國之光到辱華】一句「中國是充斥謊言的國家」　金球獎最佳女導演趙婷幾確定被封殺 |url=https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?Type=196&SerialNo=107955 |publisher=[[上報|上報]] |date=2021-03-07 |accessdate=2022-02-22 |archive-date=2022-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610132913/https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?Type=196&SerialNo=107955 }}</ref>，先是[[微博|微博]]屏蔽有关话题<ref>{{cite web |last1=Davis |first1=Rebecca |title=Chloe Zhao’s ‘Nomadland’ Censored by China After Nationalist Backlash |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/chloe-zhao-nomadland-china-censorship-1234922882/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2021-03-06 |date=2021-03-05 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320213231/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/chloe-zhao-nomadland-china-censorship-1234922882/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[豆瓣|豆瓣]]也暂时下架影片<ref>{{Cite web|title=无依之地|url=https://search.douban.com/movie/subject_search?search_text=%E6%97%A0%E4%BE%9D%E4%B9%8B%E5%9C%B0&cat=1001|access-date=2021-09-27|work=豆瓣电影|archive-url=https://archive.today/20210927151742/https://search.douban.com/movie/subject_search?search_text=%E6%97%A0%E4%BE%9D%E4%B9%8B%E5%9C%B0&cat=1001|archive-date=2021-09-27}}</ref>。中国各地的电影院在舆论压力之下，由[[广电总局|广电总局]]取消上映无依之地<ref>{{cite web |title=怎么看待赵婷的无依之地被下架？赵婷到底做了什么？ |url=http://www.shangc.net/article/2021/0502/1777058.html |publisher=尚之潮 |date=2021-05-02 |accessdate=2022-02-22 |archive-date=2022-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220222203831/http://www.shangc.net/article/2021/0502/1777058.html }}</ref>。

4月25日，[[第93屆奧斯卡金像獎|第93屆奧斯卡金像獎]]頒獎典禮當天，《無依之地》得獎及導演[[趙婷|趙婷]]資訊在[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]被大面積刪除，不少網友采用“Normad-land”、“無1之地”、“克洛伊·趙”（趙婷外文名Chloé Zhao音譯）等別稱發布信息，規避[[中华人民共和国审查制度|當局的審查]]<ref>{{cite web |title=「有靠之天」那個女孩到底是誰？趙婷《游牧人生》奪奧斯卡中國大陸靜悄悄！ |url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E9%9D%A0%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%A9%E3%80%8D%E9%82%A3%E5%80%8B%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E8%AA%B0%EF%BC%9F%E8%B6%99%E5%A9%B7%E3%80%8A%E6%B8%B8%E7%89%A7%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%A5%AA%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E9%9D%9C%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%EF%BC%81-093225126.html |website=Yahoo奇摩新聞 |accessdate=2021-04-26 |date=2021-04-26 |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429200635/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E9%9D%A0%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%A9%E3%80%8D%E9%82%A3%E5%80%8B%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E8%AA%B0%EF%BC%9F%E8%B6%99%E5%A9%B7%E3%80%8A%E6%B8%B8%E7%89%A7%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%A5%AA%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E9%9D%9C%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%EF%BC%81-093225126.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 迴響 ==
《无依之地》獲得媒體和影評家的高度評價，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據202條評論，持有97%的新鮮度，平均得分9／10<ref name=RT>{{Cite web |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nomadland |title= Nomadland (2020) |website= [[爛番茄|爛番茄]] |accessdate= 2021-01-01 |archive-date= 2021-01-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210106204601/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nomadland |dead-url= no }}</ref>，在該網站的2021年度百大電影中獲得最高積分，排行榜首<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt?year=2021|title=TOP 100 MOVIES OF 2021|website=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2022-05-04|archive-date=2022-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220613185318/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt?year=2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了平均96分（满分100分），意味着“盛赞”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/nomadland |title=Nomadland Reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2020-12-26 |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216001815/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/nomadland |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

